SPA - Single Page Application
.NET NET CORE 8 CLI, SVELTE 6 - TYPESCRIPT and DATAGRIP/SYBASE 6 start-up project

Requirements:
1. Knowledge of C# API and Svelte 6 - TypeScript
2. Node 22.19.0 and NPM 10.9.3
3. DATAGRIP/SYBASE Docker Container
4. Bootstrap 5.3.7, JQuery and Axios
5. Visual Studio Code
6. Install Google or Microsoft Authenticator in your Mobile Phone

Features :
1. Authentication and Authorization
   BryCrypt, JWT
2. TimeBased One Time Password Authenticator or MFA
3. User Profile Picture upload/update
4. Product Listings/Catalogs/Search and Pagination
5. User Account Activation via Email
6. Auto Mapper Dependency Injection
7. Swagger RESTful API Documentation
   https://localhost:7286/swagger/

If you want to test, do the following:
1. Setup DATAGRIP/SYBASE Docker container
2. Change Username and Password in appsettings.json, SYBASE connection settings
